Astro/FITS/CFITSIO/CheckStatus version 0.01
===========================================

This module provides a method to automatically catch status errors
returned by the CFITSIO library (which reads FITS formatted data
files).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Astro::FITS::CFITSIO

It will use these if available:

   Log::Log4perl


